com.damnhandy.uri.template.jackson.datatype

Class UriTemplateModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.Module
      • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.module.SimpleModule
        • com.damnhandy.uri.template.jackson.datatype.UriTemplateModule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.fasterxml.jackson.core.Versioned, Serializable

    public class UriTemplateModule
extends com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.module.SimpleModule
    Uri Template module for Jackson. To use it, simpley register it with an ObjectMapper like so: 
     ObjectMapper mapper = new ObjectMapper();
 mapper.registerModule(new UriTemplateModule());
    Any mapped JSON property that is a UriTemplate will be serialized or deserialized properly.
